de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.syntax
Class SubcategorizationFrameSet

java.lang.Object
  de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.syntax.SubcategorizationFrameSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
IHasID, java.lang.Comparable<SubcategorizationFrameSet>
public class SubcategorizationFrameSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements IHasID, java.lang.Comparable<SubcategorizationFrameSet>

SubcategorizationFrameSet is a class representing a set of syntactic constructions, represented by SubcatFrameSetElement instances. A SubcategorizationFrameSet can inherit attributes from another more generic SubcategorizationFrameSet. Therefore, it is possible to integrate a hierarchical structure of SubcategorizationFrameSet instances.

Author:
Zijad Maksuti, Judith Eckle-Kohler
